Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.37,0:00:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another trap, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.77,0:00:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Yuma!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!! What is wrong with you, Yuma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IV...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and now Shark...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.49,0:00:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of you, Yuma!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what's this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that this is our battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.62,0:01:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, satisfy me, Yuma!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With our Duel, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.83,0:01:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, what scenery do you suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}awaits us on the other side of this hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, let's climb it together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too late for us to turn back now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come to combine\N together the power dwelling inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta release my Soul Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep running, keep running, until you get there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, once again, keep those challenges coming
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My friends, keep on living in the here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep pressing onward together no matter what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heart Burning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So who will be the last entrant in the finals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will it be Yuma Tsukumo or will it be Gauche?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The field the two will be battling in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is the Dangerous Canyon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:29.31,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(66,450)}Number 59: A Fierce Fight! Yuma VS Gauche:\N This is My Manly Dueling Soul!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Duel!!\N --Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(638,525)}I'll take the first move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(637,490)}It's my turn! Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(650,523)}I Summon Heroic Challenger - Double Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoa! Due to the Field Magic's effects,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gauche has suddenly received 200 points of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:04:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Due to this field, when a Monster is Summoned or declares an attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The player receives 200 points of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the more you attack, the more your Life is depleted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-? That's really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I only have 100 Life points to boot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it? Did you like my little present, Gauche-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. So that's your little gimmick, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Droite and I were kids, we were picked up by Mr. Heartland.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He then taught us how to Duel and always did what we asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But after seeing his--Yuma's Dueling style,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it reignited my burning Dueling spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the Duels I crave for!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Double Lance's effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When used to Xyz Summon a Heroic Champion,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it counts as two materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay my now {\i1}two{\i0} Level Four Double Lances!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I build the Overlay Network and Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth!\N Heroic Champion - Gandiva!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He completely disregarded the Field Magic's effect damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I set two cards face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now bring it, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me that spirit of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't attack blindly due to how low my Life is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you hesitating, Yuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's all pumped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do our best...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get what you're trying to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now you'll take my Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroic Gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my opponent's Life is less than 2000,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it changes it to 4000 Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he boost my Life?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can draw two cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd he change Yuma's Life to 4000?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell is this all about, pal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I wanted was to draw some cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's not my style to hunt down weak prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To think that Gauche gave Yuma some Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's giving his all in this Duel, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a Monster in Face-Down Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, you can't win against him with just defending!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! I got a little plan of my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now set a card and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, taking quite the defensive stance, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Heroic Challenger - Night-Attack Kantera!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! He got 200 more damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Night-Attack Kantera to attack your Face-Down Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can destroy a Monster in Face-Down Defense Mode...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...without conducting Battle Damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now your field is empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gandiva can attack you directly now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Mog Mole is destroyed, it can be Special Summoned in Face-Up Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That little attack that cost you 400 Life Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was all a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you! You ruined the mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Gandiva's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By detaching one Overlay Unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can destroy a Level Four or lower Monster that was Special Summoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna fight cowardly, I'll crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go, Gandiva! Direct Attack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate! Battle Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It destroys the battling Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and ends the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop defending this mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate! Battler's Pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It negates and destroys a card that ends the Battle Phase!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go, Gandiva!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't beat me with that spirit of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't afford to lose this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, you just can't win this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you're being too cautious, you fear winning in this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably from watching Kaito's and Shark's Duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to you watching, you must've developed a fear of Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm afraid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Gagaga Magician!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And from my hand, I activate One-Shot Wand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card raises the Attack Power of a Magician-Type Monster by 800 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Gagaga Magician's Attack Power is higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Gandiva!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This mood won't work with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate! Heroic Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you attacked Heroic Champion,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Heroic Challenger's Attack Power is doubled,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and becomes the attack target!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the Monsters aren't destroyed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate One-Shot Wand's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By destroying this card when a battle has finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can draw one card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I Summon Grandran!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When there is an Xyz Monster on my opponent's field,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon him from my hand in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I Overlay my Level Four Gagaga Magician and Grandran!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I build the Overlay Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth!!\N Gagaga Gunman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? In Defense Mode?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious that he put him in Defense Mode to avoid taking damage from the Field Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Gagaga Gunman is in Defense Mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once per turn, by detaching an Overlay Unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.36,0:11:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I inflict 800 points of damage to my opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! How 'bout that, Gauche?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set two cards and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How 'bout that? That was such a cheap attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna have such a lame Duel with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my hand, I activate the Equip Magic, Xyz Crowned Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card makes the Xyz Monster's Rank to a Level and is treated as two Xyz Material.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Using an Xyz Monster to Xyz Summon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay my Level Four Night-Attack Kantera and my, now {\i1}two{\i0} Gandivas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I build the Overlay Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth!\N Heroic Champion - Kusanagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really wish to defeat me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show how you truly Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I truly Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The {\i1}true{\i0} way to Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see what he means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now matter the circumstance, Gauche kept his Dueling style as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all I've done...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I set a Monster in Face-Down Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How 'bout that, Gauche?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Yuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off, Kotori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going alone from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way he Duels...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta give it my all against him, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well go win and pick me up afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt that Shark and Kaito are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They also possess fearsome power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To people like them, even you are feeling fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand how you feel enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But haven't you always overcome that fear, and come all this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral... Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I have to Duel in my own way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I will let you to see my {\i1}real{\i0} Dueling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! So you're finally acting serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card from my hand, Fighter’s Charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can switch a Monster from Defense Position to Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this turn, its Attack Power becomes the same as its Defense Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I attack Gagaga Gunman with the 2500 Attack Power Kusanagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Trap, Overlay Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the End Phase, this card increase one Monster’s Attack Power by 500!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By detaching one Overlay Unit, Kusanagi can negate the activation and effect of a Trap Card,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and gain 500 Attack Points during this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.31,0:15:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3000 Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish it, Kusanagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their difference in Attack Power is now reversed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Kusanagi! Attack Gagaga Gunman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream on! I activate the Quick-Play Magic, Fighting Bond!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It negates one Monster’s destruction in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still receive damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set two cards, and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! Now you only have 600 Life left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About ready to give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real match begins now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! That's the mood I wanted from you all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:16:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a new Field Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battleground of the Setting Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only battle with one Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a Monster is destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it inflicts 300 points of damage to that player.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this... Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack Kusanagi with Gagaga Gunman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do with that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine has higher Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Gagaga Gunman is in Attack Position,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by detaching one Overlay Unit, it gains 1000 Attack Points,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and lowers the Monster my opponent controls by 500!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Gagaga Gunmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Trap, Heroic Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I activate Kusanagi’s Monster Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I negate the Trap I just activated,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and increase Kusanagi’s Attack Power by 500!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you defeated my Kusanagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, you're not half bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right back at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this will be our final battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Trap, Xyz Hotblooded Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When an Xyz Monster is destroyed by battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by paying 1000 LP, both players can use the destroyed Xyz Monster as the material,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Special Summon an Xyz Monster with the same rank!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Summon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth! Heroic Champion Excalibur!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:19:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Xyz Monster Summoned by this effect will be destroyed after the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So bring it, Yuma!\N It's your turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon Aspiring Emperor - Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be any fun if you don't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both duke it out with our aces!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to fight against a Number?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine... I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth! Number 39!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiring Emperor - Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Aspiring Emperor - Hope attacks Excalibur!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Excalibur's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During a battle, I detach all of its Overlay Units
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to double its Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got 4000 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Hope's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rune Barrier!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He protected me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, once the battle ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,due to Xyz Hotblooded Battle’s effect, the Monsters will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to the Field Magic's effect, you will take 300 points of damage and lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I still have this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Quick-Play Magic from my hand, Double-Up Chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a Monster’s attack is negated,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it can double its Attack Power and attack once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! 5000 Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Hope Sword Double Slash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one who advanced to the Final is…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuma Tsukumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Droite... I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, your mood is simply great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, if I ever catch you Dueling without a good mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat the hell outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this card...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we call a “Duelist” also means to inherit the loser’s feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He entrusted his feeling towards Dueling to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:22:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Gauche. I'll definitely inherit your feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.37,0:22:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Please do, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, Yuma! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move on ahead, speeding up our throbbing beats
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.86,0:22:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen boys and girls, here's the secret to boys and girls like you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really just so spontaneous, wild as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.74,0:22:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You might be a handful, but what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.33,0:22:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be up to no good, but learn for real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.96,0:22:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go the unpredictable route and shuffle your cards with a goal in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.21,0:23:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever you feel like you've lost your way, just take a minute to close your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.47,0:23:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shout "stop!" with all you've got, and there's your boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.65,0:23:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just stop here, not when we don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we get hurt, we can't just hesitate now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.45,0:23:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just give up, not when our future's a lot brighter than our today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.83,0:23:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriousness... It'll only make us keep fighting even harder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always get as fascinated as we want, and we'll fight on every day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Duel Carnival Tournament Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who advanced are: Kaito, Shark, Tron, and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:24:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who my opponent is, I have to find a way to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My deck's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, you're such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto is above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.00,0:24:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave this to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You… Are you really okay with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.63,0:24:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Overture Towards the Final Battle:\N The New Foe Dr. Faker!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Dr. Faker?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.94,0:24:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's today's introduction!\N Straight out of the Gagaga Academy, our new friend, Gagaga Gunman!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.68,0:24:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gagaga Academy? When did we name it that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.23,0:24:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we nominated you as the university's principle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.15,0:24:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Principle Astral.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.61,0:24:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really did become it!
